{"title":"夏天（童话诗）","authors":["圣野"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":7,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天（童话诗）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圣野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄的，悄悄的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我像一个活泼泼的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱爬竿子的绿孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸着小腿儿到处爬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬呵，爬呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给树添上绿叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬呵，爬呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给葡萄架披上绿纱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬呵，爬呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给墙绕上绿藤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬呵，爬呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给小山坡穿上绿衣……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们都爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这么夸奖我："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一个绿孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真勤劳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们看她不见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸她不着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，我们确实知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——她给我们带来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么凉爽的绿颜色！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个常常"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在洒满绿荫的窗口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看书的学生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我取个名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说我的名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就叫夏天"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}